sources.title: Conqueror Of The Orient
sources.description: 1960 directed by Tanio Boccia starring Gianna Maria Canale, Rik Battaglia, Irene Tunc, Edda Ferronao, Attilio Torelli, Ricacrdo Ferri, Paul Muller, Tatiana Farnese, Franco Balducci, Giulio Donnini and Fosco Giachetti.   The evil tyrant Dakar is taxing the people to death because he enjoys it.   Meanwhile, the busty lust-wench Princess Fatima, who is slated to marry the squeamy weasle, is repulsed by the evil Dakar and just doesn’t want to marry him, mostly because he stinks.   She’s in love with the goodly Nadir, who wants to lead a rebellion against Dakar.   Fortunately, Nadir’s father has a stash big enough to finance an army.
